This mod adds a new NPC to East Scarp. A friendly writer who happens to be Elliott's uncle.

State.Description: Very basic Content Patcher pack that allows the bachelor/ette pairings to continue hanging out, even when the player has a higher friendship level than six with either of them.

State.Author: aedenthorn
State.Description: Lets you resize the double bed and change the transparency of the bed's blankets.
State.Name: Bed Tweaks

State.Description: Lets you tweak lightning rod and lightning strike settings.
State.Name: Better Lightning Rods

State.Name: Better Ranching

Original.Name: Boarding House and Bus Stop Extension-4120-4-0-15-1679092571.zip

State.Description: Lets you buy and place multiple farm animals without leaving the placement screen.

State.Author: DestyNova and KittyCatCasey
State.Description: Introducing the "sorcery" half of "Swords & Sorcery," Hector is an eclectic druid living in East Scarp's deepest mountains. Can you unravel the mystery of a sheep in wolf's clothing?
State.Name: Circle of Thorns - NPC Hector

State.Author: Medinaquirin
State.Description: A dedicated crafting station for coffee.  Now with PFM version.
State.Name: Coffee Maker

State.Author: ncarigon

State.Name: Copper Still

State.Author: Digus
State.Description: Adds a way to customize the casks. It comes configurable with Pickles and Maple Syrup but can be changed to add any 'Object' and change the time of the products that already work on casks. You can also enable casks to work outside the cellar.

State.Author: aedenthorn
State.Description: Allows content patcher mods to create customized versions of ExtraDialogue and some StringsFromCSFiles strings

State.Author: spacechase0
State.Description: Fixes NPC spawning in custom locations, pathing to custom locations, and schedules for new NPCs.
State.Name: Custom NPC Fixes

State.Author: aedenthorn
State.Description: A combined remake of Custom Spouse Patio and Custom Spouse Patio Wizard for 1.5.5+. Now with the ability to place spouse patios on any map!
State.Name: Custom Spouse Patio Redux

State.Author: DaisyNiko
State.Description: just the tilesheets
State.Name: DaisyNiko's Tilesheets

State.Author: spacechase0 and ParadigmNomad
State.Description: Adds mannequins you can use to display your clothes.
State.Name: Displays

State.Author: Airyn and the DSV Team
State.Description: Adds ethnic, cultural, body type, ability, and gender diversity to Pelican Town, with complete seasonal outfits for all villagers! Seasonal outfits can be used for both vanilla designs & alternate designs.
State.Name: Diverse Stardew Valley - Seasonal Outfits (DSV)

State.Author: LavenderSkelly
State.Description: Replaces Dwarf's Portrait and Several other Dwarf NPC's Portraits as well.
State.Name: Dwarf Portrait Replacement

State.Author: LemurKat and Kdau
State.Description:
Welcome to East Scarp! 

An expansion adding new NPCs; new locations; new fish; shops; special orders - and secrets.

In a picturesque location by the sea.
State.Name: East Scarp

State.Author: LemurKat and Kdau
State.Description:
Welcome to East Scarp! 

An expansion adding new NPCs; new locations; new fish; shops; special orders - and secrets.

In a picturesque location by the sea.
State.Name: East Scarp

State.Author: EideeHi
State.Description: Customizable Mod for easy fishing.
State.Name: Eidee Easy Fishing

State.Author: Elle
State.Description: Adds seasonal overlays to vanilla farm buildings
State.Name: Elle's Seasonal Vanilla Buildings

State.Author: TheMightyAmondee
State.Description: Limit the amount of events seen in a day or in a row to increase story immersion.
State.Name: Event Limiter

State.Author: Cherry
State.Description: A utility mod built on top of the game's preconditions system to offer a conditions system any mod can use
State.Name: Expanded Preconditions Utility

State.Author: Esca-MMC
State.Description: Farm Type Manager is a spawning framework that allows players and modders to spawn customizable features from Stardew's farm types. It can automatically create forage, ore, monsters, and large objects (stumps, boulders, meteors, etc) at any location in the game.
State.Name: Farm Type Manager (FTM)

State.Author: farmerjack
State.Description: An all-in-one, configurable combination of my old bachelor and bachelorette dialogue expansions!  Currently featuring more than 1200 additional unmarried lines for Abigail, Emily, Leah, Penny, Harvey, Haley, Shane, and Elliott.
State.Name: farmerjack's Dialogue Expansions

State.Author: gaussfire
State.Description: Increases movement speed on placed paths, including while on your horse (configurable). By default, also provides this path speed boost when not on the farm.
State.Name: Faster Path Speed

State.Author: East Scarp Development Team
State.Description: Fievel the Hat Mouse finds a home in East Scarp! Can you help him learn not to be afraid of cats? Join him and other ES critters on a wholesome, hat-tastic adventure!
State.Name: Fievel Goes East Scarp - Hat Mouse NPC

Original.Name: Fix TVs On Custom Farm Types-12717-1-0-0-1657161819.zip

State.Author: mouse
State.Description: This mod scans for broken TVs in farmhouses and cabins and replaces them with working ones. Most players do not need this, but since it only checks if the current farm map is defining its own starting furniture instead of using defaults, it should be harmless to leave installed.
State.Name: Fix TVs On Custom Farms

State.Author: revenorror
State.Description: A simple Producer Framework Mod plugin that changes mead's name and price based on the type of honey used.
State.Name: Flower Meads

State.Author: James Clawk
State.Description: Villagers will now take notice when you befriend their friends and family, increasing (or, in rare cases, decreasing) your friendship with them in the process.
State.Name: Friend of a Friend

State.Author: desto
State.Description: Inhabitants will like items less each time you gift them that same item. Stop littering them with low-effort gifts!
State.Name: Gift Decline

State.Author: Gervig91
State.Description: Adds a unique Golden Coconut tree to the game.
State.Name: Golden Coconut Tree

State.Author: Draylon
State.Description: A Hilly Forest Map, With Wild Seed Weeds, Forest Forage, Town Fish and a Small Quarry. (Custom Farm Type)
State.Name: Hilltop Grove

State.Author: fwippy
State.Description: Adds huckleberries to the valley in mid-summer.  Requires Bush Bloom Mod and Json Assets
State.Name: Huckleberry Season

State.Author: beyondrecovery
State.Description: Makes Sandy more immersive by giving her a more dynamic schedule, more events, and more dialogue, with optional Sandy/Emily rival hearts events!
State.Name: Immersive Sandy

State.Author: Jen
State.Description: A cellar that is both home-y and can store your casks.
State.Name: Jen's Cozy Cellar

Original.Name: Juliet and Jessie the JojaMart Clerks-6398-1-4-10-1685865104.zip

State.Author: LemurKat
State.Description:
Juliet is a troubled young woman exiled to Pelican Town for reasons unknown, but possibly linked to her sharp-tongue and flirty, irrepressible nature. Her

co-worker, housemate, and friend, Jessie is matronly, empathic, and a keen gardener and herbalist.
State.Name: Juliet and Jessie the Joja Clerks

State.Author: Arknir27
State.Description: Adds Lavril to East Scarp. A mysterious young girl and her haunted toy rabbit wake up in total darkness, where evil monsters and specters of the past haunt the realm of the living... Vincent also happens to wander in by mistake. A cute Indie horror RPG.
State.Name: Lavril - East Scarp NPC (King's Raid)

State.Author: aedenthorn
State.Description: Throttles repeated identical messages in the SMAPI log, with options to throttle similar or too quick messages as well, and always allow specified sources.
State.Name: Log Spam Filter

State.Author: Lumisteria
State.Description: This mod is a resource mod for map modder adding a new tilesheet containing various buildings to use in their map. Pls read the instructions to know how the mod works !
State.Name: Lumisteria Tilesheets - Outdoor

State.Author: Rafseazz
State.Description:
VISUAL OVERHAUL UPDATE!

Adds lots of new content! From custom NPCs to new locations to even more!!

Check description below!
State.Name: Lunna - Astray in Stardew Valley

State.Author: 7thAxis
State.Description: Adds a new shadow guy NPC to East Scarp!
State.Name: Lurking in the Dark - NPC Sen (East Scarp)

State.Author: DecidedlyHuman
State.Description: This mod does nothing on its own. Its primary purpose is to allow map authors to spice up their maps with the new custom tile properties, extra features, etc., that this mod adds.
State.Name: Mapping Extensions and Extra Properties (MEEP)

State.Author: tlitookilakin
State.Description: No more boring, tidy rows of crops! Adds a random offset to each crop to give your fields a wilder look. Can be disabled for trellis crops.
State.Name: Messy Crops

State.Author: LemurKat
State.Description:
Jas is a lonely child, with only Vincent to play with, and the two adults in her life having little time with her, so what she needs is an animal friend.



Introducing, Mister Ginger!
State.Name: Mister Ginger (cat NPC)

State.Author: ceruleandeep
State.Description: Tired of watching your Multiple Spouses smooching all the time? Ever wish they could take a break for like 2 minutes? Nah, me neither. But this mod at least gets them saying cute things in between snogging, pashing, and making out.
State.Name: Multiple Spouse Dialogs

Original.Name: NEA - Maintenance only until Sword and Sorcery-12369-1-9-9-1695491674.zip

State.Author: DestyNova
State.Description: Introducing the "swords" half of "swords and sorcery" to East Scarp! Befriend our resident rogue, Mateo, as they embark on their thrilling expedition into an all new era of adventures.
State.Name: Never Ending Adventure - NPC Mateo

State.Author: Bouhm and Pathoschild
State.Description: See NPC and players on the map, with an optional minimap.
State.Name: NPC Map Locations

State.Author: Agent Lyoko
State.Description: Help save the Saloon and open Stardrop Breakfast for business! An series of events, special orders, and immersive schedules revolving around the Saloon.
State.Name: Part of a Saloon Breakfast

State.Author: shekurika
State.Description: Allows to make the things needed for achieving Perfection easier.
State.Name: Perfection Tweaker

State.Author: aedenthorn
State.Description: Provides a dialogue option to manually initiate a baby event with an NPC or player spouse when going to sleep.
State.Name: Planned Parenthood

State.Author: igotnousername
State.Description: Stops time when you wake up, and when you are in the house after 1:00 AM.
State.Name: Prepare for New Day

State.Author: Lemurkat
State.Description: After becoming the laughing stock of his peers for his 'outrageous' theories regarding the smoluanu, geologist Professor Jasper Thomas has returned to Pelican Town.  Can you help him overcome his embarrassment? Or will he fall prey to his obsession?
State.Name: Professor Jasper Thomas

State.Author: aedenthorn
State.Description: Makes the random name generator use realistic names based on predefined lists.
State.Name: Realistic Random Names

Original.Name: Ridgeside Valley Better Artisan Good Icons-11552-1-0-1649166002.zip

State.Author: Meepler
State.Description: Ridgeside Valley Better Artisan Good Icons changes the Artisan Good Icons for all of the Ridgeside Fruit Trees Fruit, into custom, collared ones, to match the color of the fruit. It does the same thing as Better Artisan Good Icons, but for Ridgeside Valley
State.Name: Ridgeside Village Better Artisan Good Icons

State.Author: Rafseazz and mamaesh - Assisted by RSV Council
State.Description: Ridgeside Village adds over 50 new NPCs, a new location, new items, new shops, new festivals, custom music, custom quests, and more!
State.Name: Ridgeside Village

State.Author: Draylon
State.Description: A Hilly Map with ups and downs, and a river.
State.Name: Riverbend Farm

State.Author: cptnmatruz
State.Description: Romanced Ridgeside Village characters will take part in CC restored ceremony.
State.Name: Romanced NPCs in CC Ceremony RSV

State.Author: Shockah
State.Description: Never worry about lightning strikes again! Prevents lightning from striking any tiles or fruit trees.
State.Name: Safe Lightning Redux

State.Author: Aimon111
State.Description: Changes the appearance of Special Order Board depending on season or event
State.Name: Seasonal Special Order Board Retexture

Original.Name: Seed Maker - Better quality more seeds-14236-1-3-3-1679412583.zip

State.Description:
Extends the base calculation for amount of seeds created in the Seed Maker based on quality of the crop used.

Supports Automate and custom crops
State.Name: Seed Maker - Better quality more seeds

State.Author: Traktori
State.Description: A small mod that allows the calendar to show multiple birthdays at once. The hover text lists the NPCs and the calendar cycles through their sprites. You can customize how it cycles in config or GMCM.
State.Name: Show Birthdays

State.Author: spacechase0
State.Description: Train your skills with gold!
State.Name: Skill Training

State.Author: PurpleChickadee
State.Description: Adds the cave carrot recipes mentioned by the smoluanu (dwarf) in their dialogue.
State.Name: Smoluanu Recipes

State.Description: A framework mod used by some of my other mods.
State.Name: SpaceCore

State.Description: Adds additional possible required tags for special orders by monkeypatching SpecialOrder.CheckTag. Also adds some debugging tools.
State.Name: Special Orders Tags Extended

State.Author: Ameise
State.Description: SpriteMaster resamples all of the game's artwork to make it look smoother - a so-called 'HD' effect, and also implements game optimizations and load-time improvements to make the game run faster.
State.Name: SpriteMaster

State.Author: SailorSaturn
State.Description: Cooking recipes designed to complement existing crop mods including SSaturn's Tropical Farm, Bonster's Crops, and/or PPJA packs.

State.Author: SailorSaturn
State.Description: Tropical crops and trees for your farm
State.Name: SSaturn's Tropical Farm

State.Author: Project Stardew Aquarium
State.Description: Stardew Aquarium adds an Aquarium to Stardew Valley. Here you can donate your fish to animated tanks for rewards. Includes a large new beach location with new custom shops.
State.Name: Stardew Aquarium

State.Author: spacechase0
State.Description: A hopper upgrade to move things between chests. A mod for Automate users.
State.Name: Super Hopper

Original.Name: The Last Smoluanu A Dwarf Expansion-9642-1-0-6-1695456527.zip

State.Author: LemurKat
State.Description: Expanding on the character and lore of Dwarf, the lonely demihuman keeping shop in Pelican Town's mine. Adds dialogue, events, and a special roommate "proposal" item so this mischievous little gremlin can come live with you.
State.Name: The Last Smoluanu - A Dwarf Expansion.

State.Author: Lemurkat
State.Description: Expands the characters of Marnie and Jas, with additional dialogue, new heart events, and an actual story arc!
State.Name: The Ranch Expansion Marnie and Jas

State.Author: FellowClown
State.Description:
What good is a dream if no action is taken? 



This mod is about a woman who dreams and a town called East Scarpe.
State.Name: Traveling Dreamer

State.Author: Cherry
State.Description: Upgrade uninhabited cabins and remove their seed boxes and beds
State.Name: Upgrade Empty Cabins

State.Author: Andrew Young
State.Description: Right-click with your watering can and watch yourself water your crops! Unlike other mods, the crops won't be instantly watered. Your farmer will go crop by crop watering them, expending the same amount of time and energy as if you had done it yourself to keep as vanilla as possible, but a lot less tedious!
State.Name: Water Bot

Original.Name: Watering Grants Experience And Crops Can Wither 1.1.2-7768-1-1-2-1644509723.zip

State.Author: Goldenrevolver
State.Description: Watering crops with the watering can grants experience, also crops may die if they are not watered
State.Name: Watering Grants Experience And Crops Can Wither

State.Author: Pancham138
State.Description: More transmutations for bars. Please, check the Notes below before downloading.
State.Name: (CP) More Bar Transmutations

Original.Name: Yagisan's Bountiful Valley for Ridgeside Village-9272-1-0-5-1693390696.7z

State.Author: Yagisan
State.Description: Extends Ridgeside Village with a variety of new forage.
State.Name: Yagisan's Bountiful Valley for Ridgeside Village

State.Author: Yri
State.Description: Adds a new architect to East Scarp. Lewis wants a better town? So someone needs to do the job right! Set a strong foundation to reach unprecedented heights, otherwise our precious home will crumble and fall. Robin needs a pay raise and Yri is here to deliver.
State.Name: Yri the Architect - New Custom NPC's for East Scarp

Original.Name: Krobus Spouse Room for Content Patcher-5751-1-1-1645127672.zip

State.Author: LemurKat
State.Description: Turns the sewer into a far more pleasant place to hang out - for both shadow people and player characters!
State.Name: A Cleaner Sewer (with matching Krobus Spouse Room)

State.Author: HopeWasHere and SoftPandaBoi
State.Description: Updates and expands on an NPC named Alec, originally by HopeWasHere.
State.Name: Alec Revisited

State.Author: Khloe Leclair
State.Description: Almanac provides an in-game book with useful information about different subjects, including a long term weather forecast and when to plant crops.
State.Name: Almanac

Original.Name: Alternate Portraits for Boarding House Gregory and Sheila-14849-1-2-1-1672047455.zip

State.Author: Airyn
State.Description: Alternate portraits for the NPCs Gregory & Sheila from the Boarding House mod by TrentXV.
State.Name: Alternate Portraits for Boarding House Gregory and Sheila

State.Author: atravita
State.Description: A collection of little tweaks: don't pick up rugs if there's something on them! Place grass under things! Confirmation on bomb placement! Right click the butterfly hutch to spawn more butterflies! Gates no longer randomly pop off!
State.Name: Atras Interaction Tweaks - aka Stop Rug Removal

State.Author: Pathoschild
State.Description: Place a chest next to a machine (like a furnace or crystalarium), and the machine will automatically pull raw items from the chest and push processed items into it. Connect multiple machines with a chest to link them.
State.Name: Automate

State.Author: TheLimeyDragon
State.Description: Ayeisha is a custom NPC who works for the Ferngill Postal Service. Who has a number of delivery events of vanilla and some custom characters.
State.Name: Ayeisha - The Postal Worker (Custom NPC)

Original.Name: Better Artisan Good Icons for The Love of Cooking-10174-1-0-1637588631.zip

State.Author: MrTiddles93
State.Description: Compatibility patch that adds new icons for the artisan items from the new crops in The Love of Cooking mod
State.Name: Better Artisan Good Icons for The Love of Cooking

State.Author: drbirbdev
State.Description: Adds a skill and professions for searching through peoples trash.
State.Name: Binning Skill (Garbage Can Searching)

State.Author: Pathoschild
State.Description: Access your chests, dressers, fridge, shipping bin, and Junimo huts from anywhere and organise them your way. Transfer items without having to run around, from the comfort of your bed to the deepest mine level. Includes optional balanced mode.
State.Name: Chests Anywhere

State.Author: Agent Lyoko
State.Description: Rewrites Clint's dialogue to be less weird toward both the player and Emily and making him slightly more well-adjusted.
State.Name: Clint Rewritten

State.Author: LemurKat
State.Description: Finished the Community Center and sad that it now lies almost empty? Now it really will serve a purpose as heart of the community.
State.Name: Community Center Reimagined

State.Author: atravita
State.Description: Adds (a) dialogue keys for NPCs headed towards and returning from Ginger Island and (b) the ability to add schedules *after* GI trips. Alternatively, (c) revamps Ginger Island scheduling to allow for more visitors at a time.
State.Name: Ginger Island Mainland Adjustments

State.Author: aedenthorn
State.Description: Lets you move and customize your farmhouse's spouse room, and enables multiple spouse rooms for Free Love mod.
State.Name: Custom Spouse Rooms

State.Author: Pathoschild
State.Description: Overlay the world with visual data like bee/Junimo/scarecrow/sprinkler coverage, hidden paths and warps, and more.
State.Name: Data Layers

State.Author: MouseyPounds
State.Description: Dish of the Day Display is a SMAPI mod which adds a localized chat message and/or an in-game sign indicating what special food item Gus is selling at the Saloon each day.
State.Name: Dish of the Day Display

State.Author: Airyn HimeTarts and the DSV Team
State.Description: Adds compatibility between DSV's Flower Queen's Crown feature and ARV's NPCs Sterling, Mia, and Henry so that they can become the Flower Queen at the Flower Dance.
State.Name: Diverse Stardew Valley FQC - Always Raining in the Valley (DSV ARV)

State.Author: Asterisk555 and Elle
State.Description: Alternative Textures packs for all of Elle's farm animal mods!
State.Name: Elle's Animals for Alternative Textures

State.Author: Asterisk555 and Elle
State.Description: Alternative Textures packs for all of Elle's farm animal mods!
State.Name: Elle's Animals for Alternative Textures

State.Author: Asterisk555 and Elle
State.Description: Alternative Textures packs for all of Elle's farm animal mods!
State.Name: Elle's Animals for Alternative Textures

State.Author: Asterisk555 and Elle
State.Description: Alternative Textures packs for all of Elle's farm animal mods!
State.Name: Elle's Animals for Alternative Textures

State.Author: Ellibear
State.Description: Expands the greenhouse. Includes 3 options to choose from depending on your playstyle.
State.Name: Ellie's Ideal Greenhouse

State.Author: shekurika
State.Description: This mod adds a GUI and two commands that allow to lookup events by ID/character name. It also has a function to show all events that are available to you today in an ingame interface.
State.Name: Event Lookup

State.Author: Inmognito
State.Description:
Tree colors are more varied and change gradually as the seasons change.



Uses Alternative Textures and Content Patcher.
State.Name: Fall Colors and gradual seasonal foliage changes

State.Author: FellowClown
State.Description: A collection of tile sheets and festival patches to fix compatibility problems with other custom npc mods.
State.Name: FellowClowns TileSheets

State.Author: Traktori
State.Description: Fixes a visual bug with the item category names in cooking recipes that are drawn as '???'.
State.Name: Fix Categories in Recipes

State.Author: Airyn
State.Description: No more disappearing beach bridge at the luau!
State.Name: Fixed Luau Bridge

State.Author: aedenthorn
State.Description: Framework for allowing complex romantic relationships, including multiple spouses and roommate with spouse.
State.Name: Free Love

State.Author: spacechase0
State.Description: Adds an in-game UI to edit other mods' config options.
State.Name: Generic Mod Config Menu

State.Author: Cherry
State.Description: Make Hay Bales placed around your farm work as functional Silos
State.Name: Hay Bales as Silos

State.Author: Pathoschild
State.Description: Summon your horse anywhere (even in the deepest mines) at the press of a button or by using the horse flute.
State.Name: Horse Flute Anywhere

State.Author: Goldenrevolver
State.Description:
Make the horse the way it should be, thin, fast and useful. Put items into its saddle bags, pet it and give it water and food to befriend your horse to increase its movement speed. 



Also includes a menu to check on horse or pet friendship and adds sound effects to the previously silent horse.
State.Name: Horse Overhaul - Thin - Faster - Saddle Bags - Friendship

State.Author: fwippy
State.Description: Adds huckleberries to the valley in mid-summer.  Requires Bush Bloom Mod and Json Assets
State.Name: Huckleberry Season

State.Author: Jibblestein
State.Description:
A content pack for MinecartPatcher that adds new minecarts to certain locations for convenience and also integrates minecarts from Ridgeside Village and East Scarp into the vanilla minecart network. Placement of new minecarts also has SVE in mind.



Includes translations for Chinese, Russian, and Portuguese
State.Name: Integrated Minecarts

State.Author: Malic
State.Description:
Jade is a self-proclaimed entomologist, lover of all things magical, and generally an odd person to meet.

Fully romanceable and marryable. Can you figure out this odd girls secrets?
State.Name: Jade NPC

State.Author: spacechase0
State.Description: Lets content packs add custom content to the game.
State.Name: Json Assets

State.Author: Pathoschild
State.Description: See live info about whatever's under your cursor when you press F1. Learn a villager's favourite gifts, when a crop will be ready to harvest, how long a fence will last, why your farm animals are unhappy, and more.
State.Name: Lookup Anything

State.Author: viberrant
State.Description: Makes minecarts a content type, accessible to Content Patcher, allowing for easy modification of existing minecarts, and the ability to add new ones. Can also create new, separate networks of minecarts, and handle large numbers of minecarts in a network gracefully.
State.Name: MinecartPatcher

State.Author: MissCoriel
State.Description: Gives all NPCs the ability to respond to certain actions with custom CP mods.
State.Name: Miss Coriel's Unique Courtship Response CORE

State.Author: Airyn
State.Description: Gives George more variety in the TV channels he watches!
State.Name: More TV Channels for George

State.Author: Bouhm and Pathoschild
State.Description: Shows NPCs and players on-screen, with compass needles that show direction and distance.
State.Name: NPC Location Compass

State.Author: aedenthorn
State.Description: Lets you play Journey of the Prairie King with any NPC you are friends with as a companion.
State.Name: Play Prairie King With NPCs

State.Description: Framework to add custom rules for producing objects. Supports code and content pack interfaces.
